          <p class="text-gray-600">Fully bonded and insured for your complete peace of mind. Your historic home and irreplaceable antiques are protected throughout our service.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985]/20 to-[#FFC67D]/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="star" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#FFA985]" fill="currentColor" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">Satisfaction Guaranteed</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">If you're not happy with any aspect of your deep clean, we'll come back and make it right. 130+ five-star reviews prove our commitment to quality.</p>
